Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.50,0:00:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(182,348)\fnImpact\fax-0.5\fscy200\fscx150\fs38\shad0\1c&H30309C&\3c&HC0C0C0&\3a&HD0&\b1}Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.45,0:00:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up! Set Up! Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gin no kamen ni kuro mafuraa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A mask of silver and a black muffler
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hitai ni kagayaku Bui to Bui
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,V and V shining on his forehead
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Sutoppu! Goddo no waru-dakumi」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"Stop GOD's conspiracy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no sakebi wa nami no oto
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,His father's scream is the sound of the waves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ikari no Raidoru hikinuite
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Furiously drawing the Ridol
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa kyou mo yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider comes again today
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.20,0:00:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X! X! X!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Killed with his father by the evil organisation GOD,\NJin Keisuke is revived as Kamen Rider X.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.80,0:01:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,His mission: to preserve peace and justice by\Nfighting the mysterious agency known as GOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.95,0:01:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell, X Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.30,0:01:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So King Dark's made his move at last...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.50,0:01:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate to think what kind of\Ndestruction that giant could cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.80,0:01:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But where could his base be?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.60,0:01:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd better destroy it soon, or...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.60,0:01:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.20,0:01:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-On your left, your left!\N-Ok!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.80,0:02:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, I was just staking out the east side.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.60,0:02:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, keep it up. But where\Nare Ichimonji and Kazami?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.80,0:02:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sure they're taking\Ncare of things their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.40,0:02:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't rely on them, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.50,0:02:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he's got us after all! Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.90,0:02:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-That's right!\N-Ok, ok!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't make things any harder\Nfor the chief! And be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.60,0:02:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You can count on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.60,0:02:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-Good luck!\N-Good luck!\N-Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.60,0:02:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.00,0:02:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch it! Are you trying to make us crash?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.80,0:02:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.80,0:03:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, I beg you! My\Ngrandson... he's sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.90,0:03:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you take him... to the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.90,0:03:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's your grandson now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.90,0:03:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Our house...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.70,0:03:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, get in! We'll take him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.70,0:03:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.70,0:03:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I don't think we--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.50,0:03:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-Please!\N-...Yeah, alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.80,0:03:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,S-s-stop! That's it, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.90,0:03:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, where's your grandson exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.40,0:03:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where'd he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.20,0:03:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.20,0:03:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.80,0:03:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-What's going on?\N-Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.30,0:04:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.80,0:04:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,S-s-scorpion!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.00,0:04:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.20,0:04:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! The name is\NScorpion Geronimo Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.30,0:04:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-Why, you--! Run!\N-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.50,0:04:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You three...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.90,0:04:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...are my hostages!\NThere's no escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.30,0:04:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\i1}Closed today{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.00,0:04:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They sure are taking their time...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.10,0:04:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Extending the search is one thing,\Nbut they should've been back by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.30,0:04:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak of the devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:04:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.20,0:05:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the chief's car alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.00,0:05:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-A scorpion?\N-Listen carefully, Jin Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-GOD?\N-We have Tachibana Toubei and the girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.50,0:05:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll exchange their lives\Nfor that last blueprint piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.90,0:05:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,See you at Tama Hills!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.70,0:05:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The scum...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.20,0:05:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like there's\Ntwo on patrol. Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.30,0:05:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-Stay back, Keisuke!\N-No, Keisuke!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.50,0:05:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin Keisuke! That's far enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.60,0:06:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought the blueprint, like you wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.70,0:06:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on out, Villain Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.50,0:06:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Scorpion Geronimo? But you're dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.00,0:06:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm his son, Geronimo Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.00,0:06:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give him the blueprint, Keisuke!\NOur lives aren't worth the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.10,0:06:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.10,0:06:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How about if I have\Nthose two girls scalped?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.20,0:06:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.80,0:06:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.80,0:06:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you the blueprint. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.80,0:06:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Throw it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.00,0:06:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.40,0:06:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike GOD, I keep my\Npromises. We'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.40,0:07:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move, Jin Keisuke! The\Nmain event's only just starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.30,0:07:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You killed my father, and I will avenge him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.80,0:07:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-Coward!\N-Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.40,0:07:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.10,0:07:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Tear him apart!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.00,0:07:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Great Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.30,0:08:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it, X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.60,0:08:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-Chief, get Chiko and Mako out of here.\N-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.40,0:08:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Cruiser Big Turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.90,0:09:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's settle this one-on-one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.20,0:09:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Challenge accepted!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.20,0:09:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Geronimo Jr.'s skills are something else...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He handles that bike like it's a horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.70,0:09:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course... It must be his Indian blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.50,0:10:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.40,0:10:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been powered up,\Njust like the X Rider was!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.70,0:10:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And now you'll see the end of\Nthis world with your own eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.50,0:10:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The end of the world!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.40,0:10:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! King Dark has begun to\Nmove, and we have the blueprint!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.50,0:10:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch closely!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.60,0:10:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The X Rider is dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.10,0:10:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way we can stop GOD now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.70,0:10:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-Boss!\N-Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.80,0:11:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke, you're alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.50,0:11:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to worry you, chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.60,0:11:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I could only find King Dark's\Nbase if he thought I was dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.90,0:11:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you, Jin\NKeisuke! Take him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.40,0:11:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, Keisuke! King Dark\Ncould run wild any minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.60,0:11:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-Ok, chief. Hang in there.\N-Don't worry about us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.60,0:11:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is King Dark's lair?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.90,0:11:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you think I'd let you find\Nme without setting a trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.80,0:12:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,King Dark!! Where are\Nyou? Show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.30,0:12:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That hole is your grave! Die!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.20,0:12:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-The building's shaking!\N-And Keisuke went in the tunnel under it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.90,0:12:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,King Dark!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.60,0:12:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Die... Jin... Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.80,0:12:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Great Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.70,0:13:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-X Rider...\N-This is the end for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.10,0:13:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think you can fight King\NDark with that tiny body of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.70,0:13:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-What?\N-Destruction Ray!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.70,0:13:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.40,0:13:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.70,0:13:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's clean up the waste first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.80,0:14:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Cruiser Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.90,0:14:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing... But he must have a weak spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.80,0:14:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,King Dark is invulnerable! An immortal giant!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.60,0:14:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.60,0:14:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Pesky little insect!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.40,0:14:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! If I can get in his mouth...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.40,0:15:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to be eaten, be my guest!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.60,0:15:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-King Dark just...\N-...ate the X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.90,0:15:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Contain the X Rider until King\NDark has levelled Tokyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.80,0:15:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's moving again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.20,0:15:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the control room?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.20,0:15:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Poison gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.40,0:16:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the control room!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.90,0:16:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Could this be it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.80,0:16:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Who...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.40,0:16:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider, my name is Dr. Noroi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.90,0:16:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I was your father's best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.50,0:16:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Best friend? He did mention a\NDr. Noroi... A devilish genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.20,0:16:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore... I am GOD itself!\NKing Dark is but a part of my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.60,0:17:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.00,0:17:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And now... the Earth is mine too!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.40,0:17:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.10,0:17:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.20,0:17:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see the X Rider's\Ndeath with my own eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.10,0:17:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.50,0:17:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happened to the X Rider in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.50,0:18:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.10,0:18:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,D-don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.20,0:18:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the end of GOD!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.70,0:18:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If you kill me, King Dark\Nwill explode! You'll die too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.70,0:18:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I've done it before.\NNow it's your turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.00,0:19:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.70,0:19:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Not... when I'm this close...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.10,0:19:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But I won't die alone!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.80,0:19:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He did it! The X Rider did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.90,0:19:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-X Rider...!\N-X Rider...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.60,0:20:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It exploded...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.70,0:20:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-And the X Rider...\N-...with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.80,0:20:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop crying, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.50,0:20:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...You'll set me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.90,0:20:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mr. Tachibana Toubei{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.80,0:20:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He's alive! He's alive!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.60,0:20:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The X Rider's alive!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.20,0:21:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief... Chiko... Mako.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.10,0:21:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gone on a journey in search of a new fight,\Njust like the other Kamen Riders before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.80,0:21:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to live up to my name as the\NX Rider, so keep an eye out for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.10,0:21:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back someday, for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.60,0:21:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Until then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.90,0:21:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Until then, goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.90,0:21:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up! Set Up! Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.30,0:21:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Black gloves and a red chest
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.20,0:21:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He leaves his mark in red and black
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.20,0:21:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,"Stop GOD's monstrous army!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.20,0:21:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,His father's scream is the sound of the waves
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.20,0:22:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Furiously kicking even stone to pieces
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.90,0:22:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider comes again today
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.20,0:22:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X! X! X!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.10,0:22:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up! Set Up! Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.50,0:22:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The white Cruiser ascends the clouds
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.50,0:22:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Racing even light across sky and sea
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.50,0:22:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,"Stop GOD's evil traps!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.50,0:22:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,His father's scream is the sound of the waves
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.50,0:22:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Furiously jumping as high as the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.50,0:22:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider comes again today
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.40,0:22:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X! X! X!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.20,0:23:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back someday, for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.30,0:23:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Until then...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.10,0:23:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Until then, goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.09,0:23:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,850)\fs50\pos(470,470)}The End
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.00,0:23:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.00,0:23:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X, X Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.59,0:23:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no tsukutta Kaizoogu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.59,0:23:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A Kaizorg created by my father
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.51,0:23:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tetsu yori tsuyoi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.51,0:23:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Stronger than iron
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.59,0:23:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oto yori hayai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.59,0:23:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Faster than sound
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.72,0:23:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu masuku paafekutaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.72,0:23:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,X's mask, Perfecter
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.56,0:23:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no negai ga ore no chi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.56,0:23:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,My father's wishes are in my blood
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.94,0:23:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Warui yatsura ni makeru na to」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.94,0:23:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't lose to those villains!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.19,0:23:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sakende iru ze
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.19,0:23:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He screams
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.28,0:23:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Itsu made mo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.28,0:23:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Eternally
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.45,0:23:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.45,0:23:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.53,0:23:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.53,0:23:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider